<blockquote>
<h2>Olympic football </h2>

<h3>Seminar Discussion Thread</h3><p>

Last Append: Mon Aug  5 13:22:41 1996<BR><BR>


Does anyone have any idea as to when or if football  -- as in football, not soccer -- will be an Olympic sport?  Also, how about lacrosse?  I realize that these sports might not appeal to all audiences, but they would certainly be at least as appealing as some of the events that are passed off as sports. 




<BR><BR><HR><BR><BR>

Appended by: Ted Curtis -- Univ. of So. Florida - Tampa <BR>Date: Mon Aug  5 06:51:53 1996<BR> Subject: Olympic football 
<BR><BR>
I would venture a guess that American football will not be added as an Olympic sport for many years, if at all. While the sport may be the most popular sport in the United States, it is just now starting to catch on in Europe, where the World League has given the game a big boost. But since the rugby scores ALWAYS take the limelight away from the World League scores and even the NFL playoffs in the British and European sports pages, I don't think football has much of a chance as an Olympic sport in my lifetime. 
<BR><BR>
There are, however, lots of other sports that could be added. You mention lacrosse -- that may be one. Others may include golf (though this talk has been going on now for some 50 years) and, I hear, surfing. 
<BR><BR>
We'll see soon.
<BR><BR>
Ted Curtis



<BR><BR><HR><BR><BR>

Appended by: David George -- Chambers of Judge - Houston <BR>Date: Mon Aug  5 11:34:15 1996 <BR>Subject: Olympic football 
<BR><BR>
Aside from the fact that not many people besides Americans care about football (a fact I can't comprehend), there is also a logistical problem.  It would be difficult to have a football tournement in 17 days.  How many games could you fit in there, 3?  You'd have to have a lot of qualifying tourneys before the games to get the field down to 8 teams.    



<BR><BR><HR><BR><BR>

Appended by: Maria Dennis -- Jones Day - Los Angeles <BR>Date: Mon Aug  5 13:22:41 1996 <BR>Subject: Olympic football 
<BR><BR>
Ernest-
<BR><BR>
Tell me, have you been watching those Emmett Smith commercials? 
<BR><BR>
-Maria Dennis

