<P>          Interrogatory No. 1: DESCRIBE each and every occasion before August 1978 on which YOU:<BR></P>

<P>          (d) Invested in real estate (including any investments in corporations and partnerships that dealt primarily in real estate.  In answering this interrogatory, be sure to DESCRIBE the real estate transactions referred to in documents DKRT900707, DKRT900715 and DKRT900716.   <BR></P>

